Step 7: What is Relaxation?

You'll hear this word a lot.

Suppose

Current node

u

Neighbor

v

Weight

wt

Current distance

dist[u]

Can we improve

dist[v] ?

We check

if(dist[u]+wt < dist[v])

Then

dist[v]=dist[u]+wt

This is called

Relaxing an edge.